Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Against this foe,\Nthere shall be no playing by ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming at you with full force!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using the Honored Sage Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You don't mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm summoning the two great sages!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's going to take some time\Nto summon the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I cannot release my hands\Nduring that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.\NBuy me some time until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Clumsy as I am, I shall try.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He vanished. What a bother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:01:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world did he find\Nsuch a creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that he's made himself invisible,\Nwe've got to use Barrier Battle Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... He's a hard one to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a barrier ninjutsu that senses and\Nalerts any intrusion across its boundary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw the barrier and switched\Nto a strong offensive critter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Gamaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Clumsy as I am, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite skilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all... I am clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Mister Gamaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you could do this\Na bit smoother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am clumsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to multiply each time\Nyou clobber them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even have a clue what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the doggies bound to\Na self-replicating summoning jutsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,\Nwe'd better move from this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll kill one dog at a time!\NLet's lure them into a small space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the center of the jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Were we able to lose it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That should buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're surrounded already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming! And they're going\Nto split up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} trying my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If they keep dividing,\Nno matter how hard we strike them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a waste of our energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here already?\NDamn persistent dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Gamaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,clumsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't move, Mister Gamaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's no time to summon\Nthe two great sages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm amazed\Nthere're so many of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But against the Great Toad of Mount Myoboku,\N you're all nothing but a small snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:03.18,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(754.688,586.25)}Honored Sage Mode!\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone... Along with the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's escaped for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato, you're still a novice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving your back open for an attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Shadow Clone too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time... Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Gamaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're relieved from duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's one thing after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I can't quit now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?! So fast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to attack the caster,\Nbut I need to be able to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think something\Nis strange, Mister Gamaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,too clumsy to understand\Nwhat you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He who possessed the same eyes as the Sage of the Six Paths,\N not only mastered every jutsu I taught him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,he demonstrated the ability to achieve all six changes in Chakra Nature.\N For a single person to do so is unheard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He was well versed in\Nall the mainstream ninjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and mastered them by the time\Nhe was ten years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is he only using\N{\i1}the Summoning Jutsu against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does he think I am beneath\N{\i1}the need for direct confrontation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Gamaken! You've done enough!\NI've got it from here, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lad! Why do you always summon us\Nin such touchy situations like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder Bunta gets so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw c'mon, Ma.\NNaturally, Jiraiya-boy has his reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You be quiet, Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, and I do apologize for calling\N you under these circumstances, Boss, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But lad... I thought you said you hated that form,\N saying it would make you unpopular with the ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to be particular right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, my foe has the Rinnegan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...the eyes of Six Paths?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone actually possesses\Nsuch an eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, you had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta start being able to go into\NSage Mode by yourself, Jiraiya-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to you,\NI'm still just a novice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So please lend me your aid\Nfor just a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He went through all that just\Nto summon those two toads...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there is a transformation going on\Nin Sensei himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph, whether it's Orochimaru or Jiraiya,\Nthe Sannin each have unique powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Where is the one with\Nthe eyes of Six Paths?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes must be degrading with age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He's hidden himself inside a summoning\N creature that can make itself invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be one of them\Nchameleon species.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have erected a probe barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drag them out using\Ncreature detection jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma, don't get so excited,\Nyou'll get more wrinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hush up, Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But why go so far as to summon us\Nto fight this fellow, Jiraiya-boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He happens to be\Na former student of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We never knew you had one!\NThen is he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, good. I'm glad you've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jiraiya-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Great Lord Elder had\N{\i1}a dream about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As you are aware, it is a prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shall now tell you. In my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You, who are solely pervy, will still\N{\i1}manage to become a splendid ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And in time, you will have\N{\i1}your own disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That disciple will become a ninja {\i1}who will\N bring about a great change {\i1}to the ninja world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is what I saw in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A great change?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Either great stability or great destruction.\N {\i1}The likes of which this world {\i1}has never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of the prophecy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you fighting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he did not grow up\Nin the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I heard he had died...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he couldn't have been\Nthe one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, if he is not righteous,\Nyou must kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:19:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that senile old man probably\Nmade up that prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Rinnegan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly looks like the one mentioned\Nin the legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What nasty eyes...\NI can't believe he's that child of prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will guide that revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day will come when you will be forced\N{\i1}to make a critical choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your choice shall decide which way\N{\i1}the change goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Great Lord Elder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I wonder if this is\N{\i1}that moment of selection?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time he's summoned humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned out to be\Na harbinger of destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So as your mentor,\Nit is my duty to take you down!
